name: Something About The Clouds
description:
AEN MUNERAH, 2021

(Where is the magic? Don’t wake up yet!)
The journey matters more than the goals! The aim of this series is to inspire people to live through the spirit of exploring, travelling, and wandering which is embedded in ourselves - wanderlust through surrealistic digital collages. I've captured memories in the form of mental images during the course of living and it's the world of pink that i want to be in.

Please visit www.pinktank.art for more information.
